#!/usr/bin/env pinpoint
# comments with a hash
# global settings before first slide

[images/adelie_penguin.jpeg]
[fill]
[font=Sans 50px]
[duration=5.000000]

--[fill]
A new slide

--[images/molly.jpeg][fill]
A slide with a specific background

--[font=monospace 18px][shading-opacity=1.0]
Here we have changed font, and set opacity.

--[text-align=center]
We can align text

--[video.ogv][fill]
Videos may form the background

--[text-align=right][bottom-left]
We can control
text alignment
and position

--[white][text-color=blue][no-markup]
A simple slide

--[top-left]
Text positions:

[top-left] [top] [top-right]
[left] [center] [right]
[bottom-left] [bottom] [bottom-right]

[center] is default

--[transition=sheet][top-left]
Transitions:

text-side-up
swing
sheet
slide-left
slide-up
slide-down
slide-in-left

--[command=killall xeyes; xeyes]

Enter - run the command
Tab - edit the command

